.name
ShowSlides
.type
Viewing Tool
.short
Utility for viewing slideshows.
.description
With ShowSlides, you can create your own slideshows. The program is fully
localized. Every gadget of the GUI is accessable via keyboard shortcut. There
are currently 20 effects available but this number increases dramatically
because of the parameters for each effect. With ShowSlidesPlayer you are able
to view the slideshows.
